    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required level. One factor (Test conditions, required level 3, achieved level 2) is below required level due to single displacement rate and single construct configuration tested per ASTM F1717. This gap is accepted because model influence is Medium, all three QoIs pass acceptance criteria with substantial margin (maximum E/uval 0.74), and the single test condition is consistent with standard regulatory practice for ASTM F1717 submissions. Overall credibility is sufficient for the Medium-risk COU. Decision: Accepted.",
